Fields:
- selectableVariant (string)
- title (string)
- subtitle (string)
- logo (image)
- isTransparent (boolean)
- mobileImage (image)
- desktopImage (image)
- links (array of linkItem)
- sortOrder (number)
- globalComponentSource (reference to cdnav)

Notes:
We included these fields by referencing mobile/desktop images from the instructions. We also have a typical nav structure with links, a potential logo, and a title/subtitle.